<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>CPDeasy - Home</title>
		<link
		rel="shortcut icon"
		type="image/x-icon"
		href="/images/teapot_1fad6_16x16.png"
	/>
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.2.0/css/all.min.css"
		/>
		<link
			href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
			rel="stylesheet"
			integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		/>
		
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
	</head>

	<!-- Start of Header-->
	<header class="container-fluid">
		<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light center">
			
			<button
				class="navbar-toggler  my-1"
				type="button"
				data-toggle="collapse"
				data-target="#navbarNav"
				aria-controls="navbarNav"
				aria-expanded="false"
				aria-label="Toggle navigation"
			>
				<span
					class="navbar-toggler-icon"
					data-bs-toggle="collapse"
					data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
				></span>
			</button>
			
			<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
				<ul class="d-flex navbar-nav fs-2 fw-bold align-items-center">
					<li class="nav-item active">
						<a class="nav-link" href="/">
							<img class="d-inline-block mr-1 navbar-brand" src="/images/cpdeasy_square.png" alt="">
							<span>CPDeasy</span>
							<span class="sr-only">(current)</span>
						</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="signup"><%= !user ? 'Sign Up' : '' %></a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="login"
							><%= !user ? 'Login' : 'Entries' %>
						</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="tos">ToS</a>
					</li>
					<li class="nav-item">
						<a class="nav-link" href="privacy">Privacy</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a   form
							method="GET"
							href="/logout"
							action="/logout?_method=POST"
							class="nav-link ml-auto"
						>
						    <%= user ? 'Logout' : '' %> </a>
						</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</nav>
	</header>
	<!-- End of Header-->
	<!-- Start of Main Page 1 -->
	<body class="container-fluid">
		<section id="home" class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row container-fluid mt-5 mb-5 align-items-center text-center">
			<div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
				<img 
				id="title-image" 
				class="img-fluid rounded-circle p-3 " 
				src="\images\lady_on_laptop_smiling.avif" 
				alt="a lady typing on her laptop and smiling, there is a latte coffee in the foreground.">
			</div>
			<div class="container d-flex flex-column col-12 col-lg-7 text-center align-items-center">
				<div class="d-flex flex-column text-center">
					<h1 class="py-2 fs-1 text-center mb-5">
						Log your learning the easy way
					</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="container d-flex flex-column text-center fs-5 col-12 col-md-10 justify-content-center align-items-center">
					<h5 class="text-secondary col-10 offset-1 py-2 fs-5 mb-2">
						CPDeasy helps you track your leadership learning journey.
					</h5>
					<h5 class="text-secondary col-10 offset-1 py-2 fs-5 mb-2">
						Adding a diary entry is fast and easy.  
					</h5>
					<h3 class="text-secondary col-12 offset-1 py-2 fs-5 mb-2">
						Keep track of your reflections and review records at your convenience with your CPD log.
					</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="btn-group py-2 md-2 mb-5">
						<div class="px-2 m-1">
							<a href="#about">
								<button class="btn btn-secondary">
									Learn More
								</button>
							</a>
						</div>
						<div class="px-2 m-1">
							<a href="signup">
								<button class="btn btn-danger">
									Sign Up
								</button>
							</a>
						</div>	
				</div>
			</div>
			
		</section>
		<section id="about" class="container-fluid mt-5">
				<div class="mt-5">
					<div class="bg-image mt-5" style="max-width: 100%;">
						<div class="position-relative text-light w-100"
								style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)">
									<h2 class="p-3 m-0">Learn about CPD</h2>
								</div>
								<img src="/images/leaders_meeting.avif" 
								alt="a trainer showing a presentation to a group of learners seated in a semi-circle nearby, they are happy and engaged."
								class="w-100 mb-5" />
								
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex container justify-content-center mb-5">
					<a href="#cpdText">
						<button class="btn btn-primary btn-block col-12">
							What are the benefits?
						</button>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="cpdText" class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-wrap flex-md-row fs-6 mt-3 mb-3 text-center align-items-center justify-content-center">
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column align-items-center justify-content-start">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-file-pen py-2"></i>
					<p class="py-2">
						Keeping a
						<a
							href="https://www.managers.org.uk/knowledge-and-insights/blog/continuing-professional-development-what-does-cpd-actually-mean/"
							target="_blank"
							><span
								data-toggle="tooltip"
								title="(Continuing Professional Development)"
								>CPD Log</span
							></a
						>
						helps leaders like you to focus, identify and reflect on learning opportunities in
						your work - guiding your progression.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column align-items-center justify-content-start">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-lightbulb py-2"></i>
					<p class="py-2">
						<a
							href="https://www.managers.org.uk/membership/chartered-manager/"
							target="_blank"
							><span data-toggle="tooltip" title="(Chartered Managers Institute)"
								>CMI</span
							></a
						>
						members and other professionals are required to make a commitment to their ongoing
						professional development and learning
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column justify-content-start align-items-center">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-book-open py-2"></i>
					<p class="py-2">
						This CPD app supports managers in that activity, providing a simple,
						structured method for adding, deleting and reviewing past log entries.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column align-items-center justify-content-start">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-users-gear py-2"></i>
					<p>
					Recording your learning experiences cements
					the learning in your mind, helping your learning and development as a leader.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column align-items-center justify-content-start">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-handshake-simple py-2"></i>
					<p class="py-2">
					CPD reflections typically make great case studies for appraisals and recruitment meetings, helping you perform better.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex m-2 col-10 col-md-5 col-lg-3 flex-column align-items-center justify-content-start">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-2xl mb-4 fa-chart-line py-2"></i>
					<p class="py-2">
					Reflecting regularly helps improve your self-awareness, greatly accelerating your learning and increasing your potential for growth.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<a href="signup">
				<div class="d-flex container justify-content-center">
					<button  class="btn btn-primary btn-block col-8">
						Sign Up For a Free Account
					</button>
				</div>
			</a>
		</section>
		<br />
		<script src="js/main.js"></script>
		<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/2.11.6/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
		<script
			src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
			integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8"
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		></script>
	</body>
</html>
